{"tid":1591404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(被死亡) 要習近平下台  湖南維權人士王美余看守所內莫名猝死","createTime":"2019-09-24T06:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T06:39:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0a2e5ffd796c78647a3cc335bd8887ea9bf778","tid":1591404,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2924733_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2924733_1_1.jpg&h=4900f4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國公民運動網報導，湖南省維權人士王美余的家屬23日收到噩耗，得知他在看守所內不明猝死。家屬相信，王美余是在看守所被人打死。<br />\n<br />\n王美余曾於去年在衡陽、長沙等多地舉牌，要求中國國家主席習近平下台，讓位實施全民選舉。之後，他於今年7月8日於長沙火車站被捕，隨後移送衡陽市看守所，罪名為尋釁滋事。<br />\n<br />\n事過多月，王妻曹曙霞23日突然受到通知，其丈夫已死於看守所內。曹曙霞在電話中哭訴，王美餘是被打死，其母親肖湘榮已經暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，王美余生前受到國保威脅及折磨，有段時間不能上網，相關圖片直到年底才公開發佈到網路，於看守所關押期間一直受嚴重迫害。<br />\n<br />\n報導指稱，自習近平上台之後，中國人權狀況急劇惡化。王美余被抓捕及「被死亡」，估計與他舉牌反習有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2924733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2924733&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=3e0ec791\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2924733&h=5444453f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2924733</a>"},{"pid":"02a148245b47411ebb20deb7fc8c4a87d8a88a09","tid":1591404,"uid":7940,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路好走"},{"pid":"c409b7c75fe3da9bbcfc57e19e115ac696568290","tid":1591404,"uid":256939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"有良知既人既下場最為悲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30bdfc7e72886fb91b1fa6f634a07f4347692f3","tid":1591404,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fe/Loberty_Day_Commemorative_0.40Yuan_Stamp_in_taiwan.Jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Ff%2Ffe%2FLoberty_Day_Commemorative_0.40Yuan_Stamp_in_taiwan.Jpg&h=50b9910d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4dd67356596085f3be7e8c8fcabc2b212cd830d","tid":1591404,"uid":31637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"講撚左而家係單方面屠殺<br />\n暗地裡64呀<br />\n正如共產黨都唔撚會認新彊有集中營<br />\n又點撚會認暗地裡64大屠殺呀"},{"pid":"2a81a2f8b15b85abb5a51fbe3de4699d96c83778","tid":1591404,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72852523234488249f92bde271b10dc51be1346b","tid":1591404,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Q1RNV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Q1RNV6.jpg&h=227effc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36616aec0e2499c38b001c7d693e78bff00705ee","tid":1591404,"uid":282777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:16:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1503199fb8a02626c8925f76949031895b0eaa0","tid":1591404,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d99d3166d05c5360032c3dae56b38afa0efeb44","tid":1591404,"uid":251414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"內地男黑獄「猝死」！耳鼻流血面目全非 妻認屍崩潰：好狠毒<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.